    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Modifies `.ts` file in shared library consumed by every downstream send-email path; introduces a new exported error class (NFR-06 uniform error contract); ProblemDetails parsing per ADR-019; touches the typed contract every Wave 1+ consumer depends on</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Touches `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/services/communicationApi.ts` which is also potentially read/imported by task 008's client-side Jest test (which depends on this task's `SendCommunicationError` export). Serial after task 002 for clean wave sequencing.</parallel-reason>
    <fr-refs>FR-09, FR-20</fr-refs>
