  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`SendCommunicationError` class is exported from `communicationApi.ts` with `status`, `code`, `detail`, `correlationId` properties.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`SendCommunicationError.fromResponse(response)` static method parses ProblemDetails and returns a populated instance.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Request type has `attachmentDriveItemIds?: string[]` with TSDoc clarifying driveItem semantics.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Request type still has `attachmentDocumentIds?: string[]` marked `@deprecated`.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Deprecation warning fires exactly ONCE per session (verifiable via test in task 008).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`sendCommunication()` throws `SendCommunicationError` on non-2xx response.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`@spaarke/auth` is NOT imported in this file (NFR-02 preserved).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`npm run build` clean in `@spaarke/ui-components`.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`npm run lint` clean in `@spaarke/ui-components`.</criterion>
